summary:
@yumebaah ha risposto al tuo post “I need a YoonKook angst with a happy ending fic, it’s been 84 years.”

 Here's some of my...
body:
@yumebaah ha risposto al tuo post “I need a YoonKook angst with a happy ending fic, it’s been 84 years.”

Here’s some of my faves (hope you don’t mind the long list 😅):

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/17697368/chapters/41745956;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/16581524/chapters/38857706;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/15999671;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/15653022;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/14973182;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/14739758;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/14757714;

 – https://archiveofourown.org/works/15965552.

I don’t mind the long list at all! Thank you so much. ♡ I will probably end up not reading them all but “from here you can almost (see the sea)” definitely has my attention.

body:
Who want an aesthetic / Moodboard ?

Rules : Send me an idol (2 max on the same / no ship please) and a Color or subject (Ex: Nature, Vampire or space). You can ask more than one (max 3). I Stan a lot of group so you can ask for a group that isn’t in the tag (if I don’t Stan I’ll try to do my best). PLEASE FOLLOW THE RULES! I can’t choose for you (subject or idol) I won’t do it if you don’t give me both, sorry.
